GitHub creds.
Removed authentication app.

Updated Django to latest version.

Updated Unidecode to latest version.
Updated Willow to latest version.
Updated beautifulsoup to latest version.
Updated django-modelcluster to latest version.
Adding nav bar to base template. Refactored handling of static assets.
Added welcome message to home page.
Added django-registration to requirements.
Navbar project title now links back to home page.
Added templates for account registration process.

Added default django authentication urls.

Configured default login page to styled user edit profile page.
Removed user attribute from the instances which were already user objects.
Hooked up navbar login form and added relevant account links.
Added missing div tag.
Modified BlogIndexPage wagtail model to allow for an about field.
Rework of BlogIndexPage to allow for listing archive of posts by time.
Added links to social media pages.
Added template tag for displaying posts. Altered routing and model attributes to simplify post filtering.
Fixed number system in post archive list.
Modified __unicode__ method of CustomUser to return full names of users when available.
Blog index page title now links back to blog for ease of navigation.
Post are now attributed by full name and link to user profiles.
Added some padding to tag links.
Added info about a users blog posts to user profiles.
Clarified the registration sign up form.
Refactored variables to make them more sensible. Removed extra unused code from blog urls.
Added preview of first 75 words for each blog post to the blog index.

Upgraded packages.
Modified requirements file to reflect package upgrades.

Added Custom User Model to Django Admin
Registered CustomUser model to django admin.

Base Template Restructuring For Favicon
Added favicon image to source control. Linked to favicon in base template. Moved Wagtail userbar include to inside body tag.

Cleaned up base html
Removed redundant CDN imports from base html file.

Redesigned Landing Page
Adding some more visual interest to the home page with a slow scaling background image. Added back bootstrap javascript which was erroneously removed in an earlier commit.
Disabled Google Banner Ad On Landing Page

Project Nav
Added a topbar nav addition for other web projects. Added a URL to a memory game web app in the new dropdown menu.

Project Bugger Addition
Added another URL to a frogger type web app in the new dropdown menu.

Starting PyTesting
Setup PyTest for django and added a basic test to ensure created custom user objects exist.
